## 🏗️ Architecture

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                    DATA SIMULATION                       │
│   Python script reads Kaggle dataset                    │
│   Sends 100 transactions/second to Kafka                │
└─────────────────┬───────────────────────────────────────┘
                  │
                  ▼
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│              APACHE KAFKA (Message Bus)                  │
│   Topic: raw_transactions  (3 partitions)               │
│   Topic: fraud_alerts      (3 partitions)               │
└─────────────────┬───────────────────────────────────────┘
                  │
                  ▼
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│         APACHE SPARK STRUCTURED STREAMING                │
│   Reads stream → Feature engineering                    │
│   → XGBoost scoring → Route results                     │
│   Trigger: every 5 seconds (micro-batch)                │
└──────┬──────────────────────────┬───────────────────────┘
       │                          │
       ▼                          ▼
┌──────────────┐         ┌────────────────────┐
│ fraud_alerts │         │    PostgreSQL       │
│  Kafka Topic │         │  All transactions  │
│  (real-time) │         │  + batch metrics   │
└──────────────┘         └────────────────────┘
       │
       ▼
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│              PROMETHEUS + GRAFANA                        │
│   Real-time metrics dashboard                           │
│   Throughput, fraud rate, latency, score distribution   │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

| Component         | Technology                    | Purpose                    |
|-------------------|-------------------------------|----------------------------|
| Message Bus       | Apache Kafka 7.5              | Transaction streaming      |
| Stream Processing | Apache Spark 3.4 (Structured) | Real-time scoring          |
| ML Model          | XGBoost 2.0                   | Fraud classification       |
| Storage           | PostgreSQL 15                 | Historical transactions    |
| Metrics           | Prometheus 2.47               | Metrics collection         |
| Dashboard         | Grafana 10.2                  | Visualization              |
| Container         | Docker + Docker Compose       | Local orchestration        |
| Language          | Python 3.10                   | All application code       |

---

## 📁 Project Structure

```
fraud-detection-platform/
│
├── docker-compose.yml         # Full stack orchestration
├── .env                       # Environment configuration
├── Makefile                   # One-command operations
│
├── data/
│   └── creditcard.csv         # Kaggle fraud dataset
│
├── model/
│   ├── train.py               # Model training script
│   ├── fraud_model.pkl        # Trained XGBoost model
│   ├── scaler.pkl             # Feature scaler
│   └── metadata.json          # Model performance info
│
├── producer/
│   ├── Dockerfile
│   ├── requirements.txt
│   └── producer.py            # Kafka transaction simulator
│
├── spark/
│   ├── Dockerfile
│   ├── requirements.txt
│   └── streaming_job.py       # Spark scoring pipeline
│
├── monitoring/
│   ├── prometheus/
│   │   └── prometheus.yml     # Prometheus config
│   └── grafana/
│       └── provisioning/
│           ├── datasources/   # Auto-configured Prometheus
│           └── dashboards/    # Auto-loaded dashboard
│
└── k8s/                       # Kubernetes manifests
    ├── namespace.yaml
    ├── kafka/
    ├── spark/
    ├── producer/
    └── monitoring/
```

