## 📊 Monitoring

### Grafana Dashboard Panels

| Panel                     | Metric                           |
|---------------------------|----------------------------------|
| Transactions Per Second   | Rate of incoming transactions    |
| Current Fraud Rate        | % flagged as fraud               |
| Transaction Throughput    | Produced vs processed            |
| Fraud Detection Rate      | Detected vs actual fraud         |
| Model Inference Latency   | P50 and P95 scoring time         |
| Fraud Score Distribution  | Histogram of model outputs       |

### Key Prometheus Metrics

```promql
# Transaction throughput
rate(producer_transactions_sent_total[1m])

# Fraud detection rate
rate(spark_fraud_detected_total[1m])

# Model inference P95 latency
histogram_quantile(0.95,
  sum(rate(spark_inference_duration_seconds_bucket[5m]))
  by (le))

# Current fraud rate
spark_current_fraud_rate
```

