## 🔧 Development

### Useful Commands

```bash
# Start everything
make up

# View all logs
make logs

# View specific service logs
make logs-spark
make logs-producer

# Check pipeline health
make health

# Restart single service
make restart-spark

# Stop everything
make down

# Fresh start (removes all data)
make clean

# Run model training
make train

# Access PostgreSQL
make psql

# Check Kafka topics
make kafka-topics
```

### Running Tests
```bash
# Syntax check all Python files
make lint

# Quick pipeline validation
make validate
```

